Pronoun <상대방에게 직접 대놓고 말을 할 때 명사, 형용사와 함께 씀>
something to say while putting your hand in someone's face.

A word screamed in public places, mainly school, church, and baby showers to upset people for your own personal pleasure and because it sounds funny.
